As the data sets are realistic in nature, there are certain noises occurred in the time series considered for this study. For instance, there is a sudden peak observed in Fig. 1g. It may affect the accuracy of the prediction and comparison analysis in the proposed method. In order to overcome this issue, the denoising process has been done strongly for all data sets as the preprocessing step by using the Gaussian process before applying the ARMA process to predict the required information.Table 4
